{"ts": "2026-05-11T01:00:00Z", "event": "feature_complete", "feature": "merge-clarify-and-research-lifecycle-phases-into-single-investigate-phase", "disposition": "not_implementing", "rationale": "Structural gate enforcement from two-file delegation is load-bearing; merge would weaken it without sufficient countervailing value. Token savings ~100-150 not ~700-900; clarity-of-flow does not outweigh gate enforcement loss. Cited retros argue for preserving Clarify, not collapsing it. Anthropic chain-prompts doc recommends chaining over collapse for sequential reliability."}
